OL,3,C'Everybody's scared': Fears over
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts as Starmer defends
OL,5,Cwelfare reforms
OL,7,FA County Durham group for people with
OL,8,Fhidden disabilities has raised
OL,9,Fconcerns about the government's
OL,10,Fplanned welfare reforms, with the
OL,11,Fgroup's leader saying "everybody's
OL,12,Fscared."
OL,14,FITV News understands that ministers
OL,15,Fare planning to announce a series of
OL,16,Fchanges imminently, which are set to
OL,17,Finclude making it more difficult to
OL,18,Fqualify for Personal Independence
OL,19,FPayment (PIP), and also freezing PIP
OL,20,Fpayments next year meaning they will
OL,21,Fnot rise in line with inflation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
