OL,7,FPIP can help with extra living costs
OL,8,Ffor people who have both a long-term
OL,9,Fphysical or mental health condition or
OL,10,Fdisability, and also have difficulty
OL,11,Fdoing certain everyday tasks or
OL,12,Fgetting around because of their
OL,13,Fcondition.
OL,15,FSu Madden, who has fibromyalgia, runs
OL,16,Fa support group called Durham's Haven,
OL,17,Ffor people living with chronic pain
OL,18,Fand autoimmune diseases, and receives
OL,19,FPIP herself.
