OL,3,C'Everybody's scared': Fears over
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts as Starmer defends
OL,5,Cwelfare reforms
OL,7,FShe said: "It's a lifeline, because
OL,8,Fwe're unable to work, it's a lifeline,
OL,9,Fit helps me get by every week, it
OL,10,Fhelps me with bills some weeks, other
OL,11,Ftimes it helps me get the things I
OL,12,Fneed.
OL,14,FSu says her group are very concerned
OL,15,Fabout the planned changes: "I'm
OL,16,Fabsolutely disgusted, why attack them
OL,17,Fthat are at their lowest already?
OL,18,FEverybody's scared, everybody's really
OL,19,Fworried about it, I'm worried about it.
