OL,7,F"I understand that they have to do
OL,8,Fsomething, but why attack them that
OL,9,Fare less fortunate? Why go for them
OL,10,Fthat really need what they're getting?"
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Joe Scrase from The Bay
OL,13,FFoodbank in North Shields believes
OL,14,Fmany more people will need to turn to
OL,15,Fhis service for help if the changes go
OL,16,Fahead.
