OL,3,C'Everybody's scared': Fears over
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts as Starmer defends
OL,5,Cwelfare reforms
OL,7,FHe told us: "It will lead to an
OL,8,Fimmediate rise in demand for the
OL,9,Ffoodbank, we will see it overnight. We
OL,10,Fwill see significantly more people
OL,11,Fneeding to access our support."
OL,13,FSpeaking on a visit to Hull today (13
OL,14,FMarch), the Prime Minister defended
OL,15,Fhis planned welfare reforms, insisting
OL,16,Fthe existing system could not be
OL,17,Fjustified.
